Bubbling Load Monitoring Applet
- A GNOME panel applet that displays the CPU + memory load as a
  bubbling liquid.
Copyright (C) 1999 Johan Walles
- d92-jwa@nada.kth.se
Copyright (C) 1999 Merlin Hughes
- merlin@merlin.org
- http://nitric.com/freeware/

--

COMPILING:

. Unpack the source:
  tar xfz bubblemon-*.tgz

. Move into the directory:
  cd bubblemon-*/

. Make the applet:
  make mode:=release
    OR
  make mode:=debug

. Install the applet:
  make install
    OR (for RedHat)
  make prefix=/usr etcdir=/etc install

. Start up the applet:
  Choose Add Applet->Utility->Bubbling Load Monitor in your GNOME panel.
